OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally dry but cloudy to
OL,6,Fstart, though there could be the odd
OL,7,Fspot of light rain or drizzle at
OL,8,Ftimes. A few cloud breaks may develop
OL,9,Flater in the afternoon, allowing some
OL,10,Fsunny spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with clear spells during
OL,13,Fthe evening, and cloud thickening
OL,14,Flater on. A band of rain and low cloud
OL,15,Fmoving in during the early hours, with
OL,16,Fstrong winds developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
