OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy with spells of rain and
OL,6,Fstrong winds through the morning.
OL,7,FTurning drier through the middle part
OL,8,Fof the day, with showers developing
OL,9,Flater on.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FUnsettled over the weekend with strong
OL,13,Fwinds and outbreaks of rain and
OL,14,Fshowers, perhaps turning heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes. Dry on Monday with lighter
OL,16,Fwinds and some sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
